# рҹҺ® WebCraft вҖ” Web-Based Minecraft Clone

## Implementation Plan

> **Stack**: Vite + TypeScript + Three.js (vanilla) + simplex-noise
> **No game engines** вҖ” pure WebGL via Three.js

---

## рҹҸ—пёҸ Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Game Loop] --> B[Physics Tick - 20fps]
    A --> C[Render Tick - 60fps]
    B --> D[Player Movement]
    B --> E[Entity AI]
    B --> F[Collision Detection]
    C --> G[Chunk Meshing]
    C --> H[Scene Rendering]
    C --> I[UI Overlay]
    
    J[World Manager] --> K[Chunk Generator]
    J --> L[Block Registry]
    K --> M[Terrain Noise]
    K --> N[Cave Carving]
    K --> O[Ore Placement]
    K --> P[Tree Generation]
    
    Q[Player] --> R[Inventory]
    Q --> S[Equipment]
    Q --> T[Crafting]
    R --> U[Hotbar 9 slots]
    R --> V[Storage 27 slots]
    T --> W[2x2 Player Grid]
    T --> X[3x3 Workbench Grid]
```

