### 4.2 Item System
- Each slot: `{ itemId: number, count: number, durability?: number }`
- Max stack size: 64 (tools/armor = 1)
- Drag-and-drop with mouse
- Shift+click = quick move
- E key = toggle inventory
- 1-9 keys = select hotbar slot
- Mouse scroll = cycle hotbar

### 4.3 HUD
- Hotbar always visible at bottom center
- Health bar (10 hearts)
- Crosshair at center
- Selected slot highlighted

