## рҹ“Ұ Phase 5: Crafting System

### 5.1 Crafting Grid
- **Player inventory**: 2Г—2 crafting grid
- **Crafting Table**: 3Г—3 crafting grid

### 5.2 Core Recipes

#### Basic
| Recipe | Grid | Result |
|--------|------|--------|
| Planks | 1 Log вҶ’ | 4 Oak Planks |
| Sticks | 2 Planks (vertical) | 4 Sticks |
| Crafting Table | 4 Planks (2Г—2) | 1 Crafting Table |
| Furnace | 8 Cobblestone (ring) | 1 Furnace |
| Chest | 8 Planks (ring) | 1 Chest |
| Torch | Coal + Stick (vertical) | 4 Torches |

#### Tools (3Г—3 grid)
```
Pickaxe:          Axe:            Shovel:          Sword:
[M][M][M]         [M][M][ ]       [ ][M][ ]        [ ][M][ ]
[ ][S][ ]          [M][S][ ]       [ ][S][ ]        [ ][S][ ]
[ ][S][ ]          [ ][S][ ]       [ ][S][ ]        [ ][S][ ]

M = Material (Planks/Cobble/Iron/Diamond)
S = Stick
```

#### Armor (3Г—3 grid)
```
Helmet:           Chestplate:      Leggings:        Boots:
[M][M][M]         [M][ ][M]        [M][M][M]        [ ][ ][ ]
[M][ ][M]         [M][M][M]        [M][ ][M]        [M][ ][M]
[ ][ ][ ]         [M][M][M]        [M][ ][M]        [M][ ][M]
```

### 5.3 Recipe Matching
- Pattern matching: compare grid contents against known recipes
- Support mirrored recipes (axe can be flipped)
- Support shapeless recipes (e.g., mushroom stew)
- Real-time preview of result

