## рҹ“Ұ Phase 8: Animals (Mobs)

### 8.1 Animal Types

| Animal | Health | Drops | Behavior |
|--------|--------|-------|----------|
| Cow | 10 | Leather, Raw Beef | Wander, flee when hit |
| Pig | 10 | Raw Porkchop | Wander, flee when hit |
| Sheep | 8 | Wool, Raw Mutton | Wander, flee when hit |

### 8.2 AI System
- **Wander**: Pick random direction, walk 3-8 blocks, pause
- **Flee**: Run away from attacker for 3 seconds
- **Pathfinding**: Simple: check if next block is walkable, jump 1-block heights
- **Spawning**: Natural spawning on grass in loaded chunks (max 10 per chunk)

### 8.3 Mob Rendering
- Simple box models (like classic Minecraft):
  - Body: rectangular prism
  - Head: cube
  - Legs: 4 thin boxes (animated walking)
- Per-mob vertex colors or simple textures

