## рҹ“Ұ Phase 9: Environment & Polish

### 9.1 Sky & Lighting
- Gradient sky (blue to light blue, darker at top)
- Sun position affects ambient light
- Day/night cycle (20 minutes real time = 1 MC day)
- Torch light (point light) вҖ” stretch goal

### 9.2 Clouds
- Flat cloud plane at y=128
- 2D noise-generated cloud pattern
- Slow drift animation
- Semi-transparent white

### 9.3 Furnace (Smelting)
- Input slot + Fuel slot вҶ’ Output
- Smelt iron ore вҶ’ Iron Ingot
- Smelt gold ore вҶ’ Gold Ingot
- Fuel: planks, logs, coal
- Progress bar animation

### 9.4 Sound Effects (stretch)
- Block break/place sounds
- Walking sounds
- Background music

